	<languages>
		<lang percentage="100">en_US</lang>
		<lang percentage="100">nl_NL</lang>
	</languages>

	<description>
		<p>
			GetIt&#39;s main focus is to make your life a lot easier when you have to test APIs or use somebody else&#39;s API.
			We know it can be hard to find a great, simple and open source application for this task that&#39;s not command
			line based.
		</p>
		<p>
			You can send numerous requests to a webserver. You can send RAW post data, form post data, add cookies to your
			request and add headers to your request.
		</p>
		<p>
			The response can be viewed either as syntax highlighted code, with JSON even being made readable,
			as the raw output, which means no syntax highlighting, and view it in a webview.
		</p>
		<p>
			Features of GetIt include:
		</p>

		<ul>
			<li>Sending HTTP requests to API endpoints and display the response of the server</li>
			<li>Saving and opening requests</li>
			<li>Easily open recent saved/opened requests</li>
			<li>Sending custom POST data</li>
			<li>Syntax highlighting for all responses</li>
			<li>Preview for HTML response</li>
			<li>Make JSON response look beautiful automatically</li>
		</ul>
	</description>

